dct_description_sm: Relief shown by 5 feet contour interval and spot heights. Map shows provincial, district, planning area, municipal or township, property and cadastral boundaries. "Crown copyright reserved." "All sheet numbers are prefixed 64/3. Thus: - 64/3/9SW4." "The representation on this map of a road, track or footpath is no evidence of a right of way." "Cadastral boundaries as shown on this map do not in any way affect the boundaries shown in Registered Titles." "300-8-59." "Air photography by Fairey Air Survey Ltd. . . . field survey data by the Lands & Surveys Department."
dct_creator_sm: Uganda. Department of Lands and Surveys
